      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cst-ctr-rig        >    w-cst-max-rig
                     move   w-cst-ctr-rig to   w-cst-max-rig          .
       z-acc-non-key-110.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione numero linea                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       12
                     w-cst-ctr-rig      giving w-wrk-ctr-lin          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione segnale di inserimento riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cst-flg-ins          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiamo routine di accettazione riga di    *
      *                  * castelletto                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-rig-cst-000      thru acc-rig-cst-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se function-key 'DELT' o 'EXIT'si esce      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DELT" or
                     v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     go to z-acc-non-key-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se premuta function-key 'UP  '              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                not  = "UP"
                     go to  z-acc-non-key-120.
           if        rf-sff-iva-cod
                     (w-cst-ctr-rig)      =    zero
