           if        w-cst-ctr-rig        not  = w-cst-max-rig
                     go to  z-acc-non-key-100.
           if        w-cst-ctr-rig        =    1
                     go to  z-acc-non-key-110.
           subtract  1                    from w-cst-max-rig          .
           subtract  1                    from w-cst-ctr-rig          .
           go to     z-acc-non-key-200.
